\",\"name\":\"Butterfly Stretch\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ibb.co/M6Bw3HW/butterfly-stretch.jpg\",\"video_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MdE_Cj6ChLo\"},{\"body_parts\":[\"Spine\"],\"calories_burned_per_minute\":1,\"category\":\"Flexibility\",\"description\":\"The Cat-Cow Stretch is a gentle spinal movement that increases flexibility and mobility.\",\"difficulty\":\"Easy\",\"duration_minutes\":2,\"how_to\":[\"Start on your hands and knees, with your wrists directly under your shoulders and your knees under your hips.\",\"Inhale and arch your back, dropping your belly towards the floor and lifting your head and tailbone.\",\"Exhale and round your spine, tucking your chin towards your chest and drawing your belly button towards your spine.\",\"Continue moving between the cat and cow poses, flowing with your breath.\",\"Repeat for the desired duration.\"],\"id\":\"F05\",\"name\":\"Cat-Cow Stretch\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ibb.co/dpbP90C/cat-cow.jpg\",\"video_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tT00XNqJ3uA\"},{\"body_parts\":[\"Shoulders\",\"Hamstrings\",\"Calves\"],\"calories_burned_per_minute\":2,\"category\":\"Flexibility\",\"description\":\"Downward Facing Dog is a classic yoga pose that stretches the entire body, including the shoulders, hamstrings, and calves.\",\"difficulty\":\"Easy\",\"duration_minutes\":1,\"how_to\":[\"Start on your hands and knees, with your hands slightly in front of your shoulders.\",\"Tuck your toes under and lift your knees off the floor, straightening your legs.\",\"Press your hands firmly into the mat and extend your arms.\",\"Engage your core and lift your hips towards the ceiling.\",\"Lengthen your spine and straighten your legs as much as possible.\",\"Hold the pose for the desired duration.\",\"Gently lower your knees back to the floor.\"],\"id\":\"F06\",\"name\":\"Downward Facing Dog\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ibb.co/54jWd5L/downward-dog.jpg\",\"video_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j97SSGsnCAQ\"},{\"body_par