 head to one side.\",\"Continue rolling your head in a circular motion, moving towards the other side.\",\"Go at a slow and comfortable pace.\",\"Repeat the motion for the desired duration.\",\"Reverse the direction and repeat.\"],\"id\":\"F09\",\"name\":\"Neck Rolls\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ibb.co/sy8cZR3/neck-rolls.jpg\",\"video_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2M80Mn0VBPw\"},{\"body_parts\":[\"Calves\"],\"calories_burned_per_minute\":1,\"category\":\"Flexibility\",\"description\":\"The Standing Calf Stretch targets the calf muscles and helps improve lower leg flexibility.\",\"difficulty\":\"Easy\",\"duration_minutes\":2,\"how_to\":[\"Stand facing a wall or sturdy object and place your hands against it for support.\",\"Take a step back with one foot and keep it flat on the ground.\",\"Bend your front knee and lean forward, keeping your back leg straight.\",\"Feel the stretch in your calf muscle.\",\"Hold the stretch for the desired duration.\",\"Switch legs and repeat.\"],\"id\":\"F10\",\"name\":\"Standing Calf Stretch\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ibb.co/Tqjm6MZ/calf-stretch.jpg\",\"video_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6vEeaK3tvzE\"}]"
    
    
